■  學習活動與作業說明 (Learning Activities and Assignments)1. Students must read the text selections assigned from week .
2. Part of the class time will be devoted to lectures and PPT presentations by the course instructor; part to discussions.
3. There will also be film viewings, documentaries and podcasts.
4. Students will engage in small group discussions regarding questions assigned by the course instructor.


