課程教材 Course Material
	    Norton Anthology of English Literature, 9th ed.  Vol. 2†

†An earlier edition of the textbook is fine, too—most of the selected works will be available—but the page numbers, of course, will be different, and it will be your responsibility to make the necessary adjustments.  At any rate, you must bring your own hard copies of the texts to class.   

